<p>Dear Subscriber,</p>
<p>This message is a notification that a new article, <%= @article.title %>, was published by <%=@user.name %>. You can access it <%= link_to 'here', article_url(@article.slug) %>.</p>
<p>If you don't want to receive these emails click this link to <%= link_to 'unsubscribe', unsubscribe_url(id: @subscriber.id, token: @subscriber.unsubscribe_token) %>.</p>